Hi! Welcome to Fiona's T Profile Page!

I'm a feminist Internet activist, fighting for privacy and openness on the Web. I have a passion for digital literacy and diversity in tech and I play a pink violin in a children's orchestra. I created the T Profile online to provide links and because I like the look of old school terminals. Thank you so much for your attention!
